Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.60,1:05:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,at 195 around there
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.70,1:05:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,mm-hmm now some of them have been taken over and big corporations that were
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.17,1:06:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,non-integrated are now over 200 so a lot of them are now over 200 and going
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.60,1:06:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,through a reconstruction no I think the average I have 100 greatest corporations
