Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.70,1:17:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,one in Dallas.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.70,1:17:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.70,1:17:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And this was like on a Monday, and I had this dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.70,1:17:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was so powerful, I called my father who was a pilot.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.31,1:17:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.31,1:17:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And I said, I just want to tell you about this dream I'm having.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.31,1:17:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know, it was about sitting in the rear of the plane in a safe place and so forth.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.31,1:17:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, well, that's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.31,1:18:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But the two planes went down, and on Friday, I called him back because I had all this doubt.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.01,1:18:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Did this really occur?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.01,1:18:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I really have this dream?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.01,1:18:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.01,1:18:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And I recognized later that it's like this is the ego covering up anything other than
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.49,1:18:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,linear reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.49,1:18:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.49,1:18:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had to literally go to him on Friday and say, did I have this conversation with
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.49,1:18:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,you on Monday?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.49,1:18:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.49,1:18:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I not talk about these dreams?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.49,1:18:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.49,1:18:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And he said, yes, you did.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.49,1:18:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, he confirmed it to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.49,1:18:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.49,1:18:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But in my mind, to me, it was the ego covering up, you know, anything that's not within
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.49,1:18:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,its realm.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.49,1:18:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.65,1:18:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.65,1:18:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know about that interpretation.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.65,1:18:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.88,1:18:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, we live in a world of infinite potentiality, any one of which, combined with intention,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.94,1:18:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,combined with karma, plus favorable circumstances, may materialize.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.96,1:18:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one of 10 million options that could materialize.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.64,1:18:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sooner or later, one of them's going to materialize.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.80,1:19:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They materialize.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.81,1:19:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.81,1:19:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.81,1:19:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Lincoln saw his own death.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.81,1:19:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it happens very often.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.81,1:19:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.81,1:19:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Abraham Lincoln saw his own assassination in a dream, et cetera, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.81,1:19:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.81,1:19:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.19,1:19:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just curious about what you thought about the idea of the ego covering all this
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.19,1:19:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,up.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.19,1:19:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you mean by that.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.19,1:19:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the same thing happened when I came up with a name, and the person across the
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.87,1:19:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,table from me was quite shocked by it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.17,1:19:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.17,1:19:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But then suddenly covered up and said, oh, well, yeah, that's my great-grandmother's
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.41,1:19:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,name who died 27 years ago, and we never met, who I haven't thought about in 22 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.41,1:19:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.41,1:19:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the question?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.41,1:19:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.41,1:19:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, is this the ego covering up this astonishment, this surprise?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.41,1:19:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did they cover this up?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.41,1:19:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, just a statistical likelihood.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.41,1:19:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.41,1:19:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why people are impressed with psychic powers.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.41,1:19:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.41,1:19:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.41,1:20:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.22,1:20:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I see your grandmother reading the tea leaves.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.22,1:20:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.22,1:20:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.26,1:20:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandmother used to read the tea leaves.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.26,1:20:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She did.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.32,1:20:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.32,1:20:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.32,1:20:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I see your grandmother reading the tea leaves.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.32,1:20:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.83,1:20:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.63,1:20:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a few burning questions for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.62,1:20:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.61,1:20:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If I tell a lie, what is the energetic repercussion of that in the hologram?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.43,1:20:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens to the person that I'm lying to?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.43,1:20:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens to me?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.43,1:20:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How does it affect all that is?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.43,1:20:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,When an untruth has happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.43,1:20:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're never going to affect all that is, you know, because you're an infinitesimal
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.43,1:20:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,part of what all that is.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.43,1:20:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But if everybody does it, then the consciousness level of mankind goes up or down.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.74,1:21:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, everybody knows unconsciously when they're being lied to.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.74,1:21:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yeah, closer.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.64,1:21:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to be on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.44,1:21:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.44,1:21:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to be where you're with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.44,1:21:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, everybody...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.44,1:21:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.44,1:21:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.44,1:21:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.44,1:21:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.44,1:21:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This side or this side.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.44,1:21:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, everybody knows unconsciously when they're being lied to or just...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.44,1:21:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.33,1:21:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.33,1:21:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So that shows you something interesting.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.82,1:21:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Because when I calibrated the advertising industry as an industry, it was below 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.77,1:21:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, think how much more, you know, how much more powerful an advertisement would
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.65,1:21:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,be.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.65,1:21:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to have hyperacidity, and I take the purple pill, and now my stomach feels fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.61,1:21:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But she's an actress, so she's lying.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.65,1:21:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't think it's somebody who had terrible hyperacidity.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.72,1:22:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They took the purple pill, and now they feel great.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.80,1:22:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,One would be convincing unconsciously, and the other you know is crap.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.88,1:22:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.16,1:22:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I used strong language.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.16,1:22:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.16,1:22:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The other is...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.29,1:22:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Advertisements would be powerful if they were real.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.29,1:22:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And if they...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.29,1:22:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, we were calibrating, I think I'm gonna, at the last minute, put in maybe half
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.69,1:22:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,a page of advertisements, you know, like the MSN Butterfly.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.29,1:22:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, he's so stupid looking, how he would sell anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.29,1:22:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the dumbest commercial I've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.29,1:22:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, Whiskas is hilarious.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.29,1:22:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Whiskas shows his little, you know, cat and shows this big stag, you know, and then the
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.65,1:22:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,kitty stares down the stag and starts to chase the stag, and the stag runs off.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.29,1:22:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You calibrate that, it's over 500.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.29,1:22:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you gonna ask me?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.29,1:22:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know how...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.29,1:22:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the fact that our thoughts, every one of our thoughts ripples through the universe.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.68,1:22:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it does.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.68,1:23:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ripples through the hologram.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.28,1:23:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.28,1:23:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So my thought would be that a lie would have some kind of a repercussion for the
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.28,1:23:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,hologram.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.46,1:23:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what about a white lie?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.46,1:23:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.46,1:23:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, the different levels of lies.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.46,1:23:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.46,1:23:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You could text someone.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.46,1:23:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.46,1:23:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, because there's...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.46,1:23:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.46,1:23:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, you could text someone.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.46,1:23:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, because there's...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.46,1:23:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, you could text someone.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.46,1:23:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, because there's...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.46,1:23:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, you could text someone.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.46,1:23:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, because there's...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.46,1:23:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus is asking a couple different questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.46,1:23:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.46,1:23:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,See, below 200 is force, it's not power.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.46,1:23:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So an itty-bitty lie at energy field 180, its impact on all of life is insignificant.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.46,1:23:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody who lies at level 520 is gonna have some serious karmic consequences.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.46,1:23:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.46,1:23:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.46,1:23:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.46,1:23:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.46,1:23:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
