Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.21,1:24:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.21,1:24:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.21,1:24:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, in certain realms, murder is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.26,1:24:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you kill 10 or 12 people,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.84,1:24:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,so what does that make you, a big shot?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.30,1:24:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You get in there with the big boys to kill 10 million,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.30,1:24:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,now you're playing with the big dealers.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.82,1:24:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The big dealers, 10 million here, 20 million there.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.08,1:24:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Mayo, 30 million die of starvation
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.91,1:25:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,due to Marxist BS, due to totalitarianism.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.23,1:25:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,People want to sell us that paradigm of reality?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.37,1:25:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.41,1:25:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've also noticed there are different kinds of lying,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.71,1:25:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,like the sin of omission.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.27,1:25:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We know the intention behind it, right.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.47,1:25:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You just reveal it all.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.85,1:25:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There's two intentions.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.03,1:25:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,One is to hurt other people.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.11,1:25:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a different karma than to protect yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.09,1:25:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes we lie just to cover ourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.32,1:25:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not really injuring anybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.04,1:25:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's lowering our own internal integrity.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.64,1:25:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then sometimes we lie to injure somebody else.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.76,1:25:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,To bear false witness is a rather grave karmic consequence.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.90,1:25:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's to bear false witness against your neighbor.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.20,1:25:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I don't like to hear the severe polemics of political extremes,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.30,1:25:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,because to falsely accuse somebody else
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.06,1:25:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,is, you know, violating one of the commandments.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.64,1:25:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not to bear false witness against yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.86,1:25:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's to bear false witness against your neighbor,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.86,1:26:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,even if he's running, you know, on the other party.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.86,1:26:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still a grave error, see.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.86,1:26:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to vilify chocolate to be the champion of vanilla,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.86,1:26:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and I wish the politics would learn that.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.86,1:26:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So if one is of a more high consciousness, like, say, 500,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.50,1:26:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and you tell a little white lie,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.50,1:26:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,what we call a white lie to protect yourself...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.50,1:26:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't get away with white lies as you move on up.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.50,1:26:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So even an exaggeration would be considered...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.10,1:26:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, white lies are...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.27,1:26:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you worrying about that?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.27,1:26:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to try and sell me a used car, or what?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.09,1:26:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What else?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.99,1:26:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to try and sell me a used car.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.99,1:26:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that discussion of integrity
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.97,1:26:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and the implications of it in business, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.97,1:26:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,came up over the weekend with the visitor.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.97,1:26:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I had me discuss the impact of that in business.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.97,1:26:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that was one of my burning questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.30,1:26:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Another one is...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.30,1:27:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.30,1:27:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.30,1:27:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,When I have the desire to pray for another person,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.30,1:27:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,how do I do that without being in a positionality or thoughts
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.30,1:27:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,or in some way judging their experience or their life
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.30,1:27:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,because I'm wanting to pray for, you know...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.30,1:27:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to change them, really.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.30,1:27:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.30,1:27:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're trying to change their spiritual destiny.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.30,1:27:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to help them, send them energy, whatever you want to call it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.30,1:27:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.30,1:27:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to undo their negative karma, or what?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.46,1:27:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I'm wondering, how do I connect with another being with prayer?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.46,1:27:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you want to connect with them?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.00,1:27:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm stuck in the new age.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.00,1:27:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to connect with any dead people. Do you?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.00,1:27:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no. Not dead people. Live people.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.00,1:27:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, live people.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.00,1:27:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, like I want to pray for somebody who is...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.00,1:27:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I got you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.00,1:27:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...having problems in their life or, you know...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.00,1:27:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you stay to the highest good, then you're doing well.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.00,1:27:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, because what you see as disaster is frankly to their highest good.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.23,1:28:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I do have that caveat in my prayer.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.74,1:28:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I say to the highest good...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.74,1:28:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.74,1:28:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.74,1:28:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,See, because the person's highest good, you can see they're speeding rapidly towards the bottom in disaster.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.63,1:28:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's just what their higher self is holding for them.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.63,1:28:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If you try to prevent the disaster, you just, you know, delayed their salvation.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.39,1:28:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it was only by hitting bottom that they are going to rise to the top.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.52,1:28:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So, therefore, trying to change it out there, you know, is being quite naive.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.52,1:28:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Because, like you said, your perception may not be what it's about at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.52,1:28:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like we applaud people's success, and that success is, you know, what's going to take them to the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.52,1:28:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We see that happen all the time to celebrities and various people.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.52,1:28:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it still worthwhile to pray for them then?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.83,1:29:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. That's what your motive is, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.05,1:29:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, you wouldn't be asking the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.05,1:29:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're trying to change people, influence them, control things.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.88,1:29:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're messing around with other people's karma and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.01,1:29:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other side is the gooderism, and on the other side is genuine spiritual commitment.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.01,1:29:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have to find out where you are and all that.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.17,1:29:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like I have a high motivation of just sending them energy of help and caring.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.49,1:29:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they ask you to do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.49,1:29:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.49,1:29:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.14,1:29:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a big one going down.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.14,1:29:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There's different answers at different levels.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.14,1:29:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But I get you're about to transcend that level.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.14,1:29:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, you wouldn't be asking me the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.14,1:29:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.14,1:29:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're trying to influence other people.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.14,1:29:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.14,1:29:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're already getting that intuitively.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.14,1:29:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you're asking me.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.14,1:29:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.46,1:29:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let them worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.46,1:29:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Let their own karma and their own be what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.78,1:30:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.78,1:30:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Your intention to be loving towards them, of course, is great.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.36,1:30:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And the last question I wanted to ask you is, okay, it's beyond the third dimension that we're in right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.90,1:30:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Third dimension?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.09,1:30:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that just a new age thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.09,1:30:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in the 9th or 10th generation.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.09,1:30:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still back in the third?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.69,1:30:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.69,1:30:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just kidding along with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.69,1:30:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.69,1:30:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.69,1:30:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The past, present, and future at some point becomes one.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.69,1:30:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not in time anymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.69,1:30:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.69,1:30:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,At some point.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.69,1:30:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So from that place, I'm assuming it's all the past, present, and future become one somewhere in the future.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.69,1:30:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,One somewhere in the field of consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.69,1:30:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they don't become one.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.76,1:30:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But they are one.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.76,1:30:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't become anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.92,1:31:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is in reference to the fact that calibrating...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.94,1:31:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,See, they're not three separate things that then become one.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.94,1:31:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.94,1:31:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They're three separate things to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.94,1:31:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, just no time.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.94,1:31:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no past, present, or future.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.94,1:31:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,In the space that we're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.94,1:31:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But with the tool of kinesiology, we are only to calibrate present statements.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.94,1:31:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.94,1:31:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.94,1:31:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So past, present, and future are all one beyond here anyway, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.04,1:31:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.04,1:31:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too much to think about.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.04,1:31:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.28,1:31:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm trying to ask why we can't calibrate the future if the future is the same...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.28,1:31:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it has no existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.28,1:31:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It has no reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.28,1:31:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know that based on your information.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.28,1:31:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But if the future is the same as the present and the past...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.28,1:31:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're confusing it intellectually.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.28,1:31:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're playing with it conceptually.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.28,1:31:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't a conceptual thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.31,1:32:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious that the future has no reality because otherwise there would be no evolution
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.63,1:32:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.63,1:32:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There would be no spiritual merit.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.58,1:32:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the universe is waiting for you to collapse the wave function.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.58,1:32:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Through the Heisenberg principle, intention itself, consciousness itself already takes
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.22,1:32:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,potentiality into actuality.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.64,1:32:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The minute you look at a thing, it's already changed.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.64,1:32:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot see the same thing twice because you're looking at it has already changed it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.47,1:32:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So, therefore, no future could possibly be known because it depends on an infinite number
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.56,1:32:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,of decisions and choices.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.66,1:32:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why you can't predict future events.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.66,1:32:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going to happen in the year 5083 is all in your head.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.68,1:32:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody can predict what's going to happen in the year 5083.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.80,1:32:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Not possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.80,1:32:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the future is only a potentiality.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.92,1:33:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Free choice means that you are where you are within the infinite field by virtue of choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.10,1:33:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You choose this.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.10,1:33:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You choose this.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.10,1:33:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You choose this.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.10,1:33:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You choose this.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.10,1:33:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If the fate was of all of the universe was already set, predetermination, there would
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.69,1:33:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,be no point to life anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.85,1:33:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So predestination is just an intellectual concept.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.56,1:33:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.56,1:33:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the same as karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.72,1:33:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they're not the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.72,1:33:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.26,1:33:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Because divinity, once you understand the nature of divinity, you realize that predestination
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.26,1:33:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and divinity are not compatible.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.93,1:33:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Divinity cannot be divinity and still be the source of predestination unless you project
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.49,1:33:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,forward into the future and now the present becomes the past.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.49,1:33:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You see what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.49,1:33:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what that meant, but it sounded good.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.39,1:33:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.39,1:33:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That should shut her up, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.39,1:34:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you get into intellectual constructs.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.34,1:34:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good question.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.60,1:34:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, she's got a lot of good questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.60,1:34:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.60,1:34:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.72,1:34:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A question about resistance.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.72,1:34:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it best to resist nothing or is there nothing to resist?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.16,1:34:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a conundrum.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.16,1:34:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you resist nothing?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.80,1:34:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There'd be nothing to resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.80,1:34:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by resisting nothing?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.21,1:34:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean don't resist anything, not nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.56,1:34:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't resist anything that comes up.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.68,1:34:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, true.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.68,1:34:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.54,1:34:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The other way is to resist everything all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:52.45,1:34:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.45,1:34:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.44,1:34:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, my main question would be that I tried the kinesiology testing.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.57,1:34:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.57,1:34:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,She tried kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.57,1:34:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.57,1:35:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.36,1:35:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But I would like to know how would I get more consistent answers or more
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.36,1:35:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,consistency?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.36,1:35:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.40,1:35:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to know how would I get more consistent answers or more clear answers.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.40,1:35:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.40,1:35:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It depends on what the basic problem is.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.40,1:35:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd have to do like a short individual workshop with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.16,1:35:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,As I mentioned this morning, the capacity to do it, first of all, not everybody has
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.90,1:35:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.90,1:35:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Secondly, it's limited to probably 10% of the population anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.35,1:35:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The intentionality, the intention behind the question has to be integrous.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.35,1:35:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I would always say in the name of the highest good, you can't have any personal interest.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.41,1:35:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't have any personal interest in the outcome.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.11,1:36:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And the background in the setting has to be appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.11,1:36:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And you may need special training.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.91,1:36:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the easiest thing in the world for some people.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.91,1:36:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people it becomes very easy and other people it's quite difficult.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.91,1:36:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Susie teaches it to a lot of people and she usually finds out what's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.91,1:36:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes they're holding the arm too straight.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.91,1:36:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I would say a lot of people resist the arm going weak.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.91,1:36:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very transitory weakness.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.91,1:36:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And the ape in us thinks it's falling out of a tree.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.91,1:36:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So you get it, especially in macho guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.91,1:36:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The minute the arm goes weak, they're unconsciously falling out of a tree and their ape comes
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.91,1:36:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,up with strength, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.91,1:36:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And they get high answers for everything, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.52,1:36:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My dog calibrates over 1,000, 2,000, 3,000.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:44.52,1:36:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We get letters all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.59,1:36:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My dog calibrates over 900, I think.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.59,1:36:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.68,1:36:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.41,1:36:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a technique.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.41,1:37:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be learned.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.41,1:37:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes there's a kinesiologist.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.41,1:37:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of times a holistic practitioner.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:05.41,1:37:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's actually a kinesiologist that you can see for a private consult.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.41,1:37:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you ever read Dr. Diamond's book?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.44,1:37:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So you need education.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.44,1:37:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Body Doesn't Lie by Dr. Diamond is a classic in the field.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.47,1:37:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So you just need more education.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.23,1:37:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, have you heard of a contemplative outreach, Father Thomas Keating?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.23,1:37:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.23,1:37:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Centering prayer.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.23,1:37:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We spoke up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.23,1:37:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We were with Father Keating a few months ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.77,1:37:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.28,1:37:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a big guy.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.20,1:37:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He's over six foot tall.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.20,1:37:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.20,1:37:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Look up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.20,1:37:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm high, brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.20,1:37:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.20,1:37:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.20,1:37:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.20,1:37:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We spoke at the St. Benedict's Monastery up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.20,1:37:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Met with monks.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.20,1:37:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And we did a public thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.43,1:38:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.43,1:38:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We did a public thing in the city hall there in Aspen.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.43,1:38:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a beautiful monastery.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.56,1:38:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.56,1:38:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful place.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.56,1:38:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So centering prayer and contemplative outreach.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.56,1:38:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.56,1:38:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the champion of centering prayer.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.56,1:38:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Which got him into a little trouble with the church itself, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.65,1:38:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But he handled it.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.48,1:38:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The classic religion distrusts the mystic.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.48,1:38:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And I represent the mystic.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.57,1:38:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So when I spoke to the monks, they didn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.86,1:38:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if they were praying silently inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.33,1:38:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The worry is that without ecclesiastic guidance, a person could go wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.33,1:39:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And that it sees authority as protective of the naive soul that could wander off into
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.54,1:39:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,wide avenues.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.54,1:39:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a certain reality to that.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.69,1:39:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't discredit it.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.69,1:39:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Certain reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.69,1:39:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we get a lot of bizarre letters out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.01,1:39:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Where people do get derailed.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.39,1:39:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.96,1:39:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I know Father Keating.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.96,1:39:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.29,1:39:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I enjoyed him, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.92,1:39:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, we had dinner with him, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.92,1:39:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.48,1:39:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.48,1:39:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Even for someone like yourself, how susceptible is kinesiology to the Luciferic?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.41,1:40:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Luciferic means, too, is the temptation of power.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.57,1:40:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember when the Luciferic came.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.57,1:40:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-verbally, as a knowingness, power for its own sake was what it was about.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.50,1:40:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what that's got to do with kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.56,1:40:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Of getting, having a Luciferic influence give you the wrong answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.56,1:40:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that would be the intentionality of the person using it.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.88,1:40:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who seeks to use it for gain, for power.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.88,1:40:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually, the misuse of it is to verify positionality.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.04,1:41:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,People want you to calibrate something they've already got a really screeching positionality
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.51,1:41:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,about.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.51,1:41:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.86,1:41:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,To verify that their candidate is better than this candidate's.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.86,1:41:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Or this spiritual teacher is better than that spiritual teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.86,1:41:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They have a vested interest.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.96,1:41:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'd say Luciferic use is a vested interest.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.96,1:41:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A vested interest.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.30,1:41:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Something to gain by it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.30,1:41:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of a tool, it's something to gain by.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.71,1:41:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But even if you have positive intentions of the Luciferic energy trying to get in there
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.71,1:41:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and giving you wrong answers?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.71,1:41:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the whole point of being Integrist.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.21,1:41:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So, because both are over 200 and the question is Integrist, the Luciferic does not prevail.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.21,1:41:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you say, in the name of the highest good.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.42,1:41:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,See, the Luciferic has a vested interest in one answer or the other.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.42,1:41:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The Luciferic is certainly not interested in one answer or the other.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:53.42,1:41:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's certainly not interested in what is the highest good.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.18,1:42:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not interested in the stockholder.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.50,1:42:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's interested in exercising its stock options.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.50,1:42:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not interested in the welfare of the stockholder.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.50,1:42:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So, yes, I understand what you're saying from a hypothetical viewpoint.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:16.36,1:42:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And I looked at myself quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.42,1:42:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have a hug?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.42,1:42:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:22.42,1:42:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have a hug?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.42,1:42:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have a hug.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.87,1:42:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to put some devious burp behind me.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.87,1:42:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, that's a very good question.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.32,1:42:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good question.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:36.32,1:42:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It shows he's not asleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:39.71,1:42:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you see he's not into denial.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.71,1:42:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He realizes that there's things out there that are antithetical to spirituality
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.71,1:42:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and purity and integrity, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.71,1:42:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And it comes looking for your chinks.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.80,1:42:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it does look for your chinks.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:57.59,1:43:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.44,1:43:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.88,1:43:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.88,1:43:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Um.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.88,1:43:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is regarding the idea of the soul moving up through evolution
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.56,1:43:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,like a cork in the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.56,1:43:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.56,1:43:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it's, I mean, personally, I feel I can see it in the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.56,1:43:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And you mention in your book that suddenly a soul, for one reason or another,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.56,1:43:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,will put down a heavy foot and start backpedaling.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.56,1:43:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.56,1:43:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the divine quality that would motivate a soul to suddenly want to U-turn?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.74,1:43:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,To suddenly what?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.74,1:43:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do a U-turn instead of continuing to evolve towards a higher power.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.74,1:43:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.74,1:43:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And suddenly make decisions that lower...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:37.74,1:43:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, because there's traps all along the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.74,1:43:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That which hates integrity is out to get you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.74,1:43:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You realize that the tremendous gain that huge parts of the population get from non-integrity,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.74,1:43:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,you try and get Israel and Palestine to quit their war, they're going to assassinate you
Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.74,1:43:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the minute you look like you're serious about peace.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.74,1:43:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Because their whole game is war.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.74,1:43:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should they like what you have to present?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.31,1:43:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.31,1:43:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.75,1:43:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
