Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.32,1:44:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.32,1:44:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should they look favorably on 540?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:24.32,1:44:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would the 540 then suddenly make decisions that lowers it's consciousness down to 190?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:25.32,1:44:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, why do people fall...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.32,1:44:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.32,1:44:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...Because, um...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.32,1:44:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There's temptations at each level.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:31.22,1:44:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There's temptations.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.16,1:44:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,When you say, I am so-and-so, you instantly bring up the idea that you're a genius.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:33.16,1:44:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You kill your enemy.
